name: Nancy Carlsson-Paige
summary: Nancy Carlsson-Paige. Actress: Stuck on You. Nancy Carlsson-Paige was born on 9 February 1944 in the USA. She is an actress, known for Stuck on You (2003), Zoom (1997) and FETCH! with Ruff Ruffman (2006). She was previously married to Kent Damon.
